==English==
===Noun===
'''canton''' (''plural'' '''cantons''')

#One of the [[state]]s making up the [[Confederation]] of [[Switzerland]].
#An [[subdivision]] of an ''[[arrondissement]]'' of [[France]].
#A subdivision of [[Luxembourg]] (the country).
#A subdivision of [[Bosnia and Herzegovina]].
#A subdivision of a flag, the rectangular inset on the upper [[hoist]] (i.e., flagpole) side; the stars of the US national flag are in a canton. 

